This fixes the generation of resource metrics to respect milli
precision.

@brancz I realized I introduced this mistake when reviewing your last PR.

We've accumulated a number of features over the past month, and since we've traditionally cut releases right around Kubernetes releases, here it goes.

I encourage everyone to test this so we can find bugs, should there be any new ones introduced.

